 value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"html\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"44\" endIndex=\"50\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>banner</code>.</p></body></html>"
